---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="快速入门 | 我应该从哪里开始？ | BVI.vg" description="根据你的身份和需求，快速定位最适合的BVI工具和阅读路径。">
  <div class="max-w-(--content-max-width) mx-auto px-6 py-10">
    <article class="prose">
      <h1>我应该从哪里开始？</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-muted">根据你的身份和需求，选择最适合的阅读路径。每个路径约需要 10-15 分钟。</p>

      <h2>选择你的角色</h2>

      <div class="space-y-3 not-prose">
        <details class="border border-border-main rounded-xl overflow-hidden group" open>
          <summary class="px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-bg-muted hover:bg-border-light transition-colors font-sans font-semibold text-base flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>我是家族办公室负责人</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-5 py-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
            <p><strong>你可能需要：</strong>多资产类别的分类管理、家族财富传承、控制权保留</p>
            <p><strong>推荐阅读路径：</strong></p>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1">
              <li><a href="/comparison/">工具对比</a> → 了解四种核心工具的定位（5分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/spc/">SPC 专题</a> → 如果涉及多策略/多资产分类管理（10分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/vista/">VISTA 信托</a> → 如果涉及家族企业股权传承（10分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/ptc/">PTC 专题</a> → 如果资产规模超过 $20M（10分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/case-studies/">案例参考</a> → 看类似家族怎么做的（5分钟）</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="border border-border-main rounded-xl overflow-hidden group">
          <summary class="px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-bg-muted hover:bg-border-light transition-colors font-sans font-semibold text-base flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>我是企业家/公司创始人</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-5 py-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
            <p><strong>你可能需要：</strong>境外上市架构、创始人持股安排、家族企业保护</p>
            <p><strong>推荐阅读路径：</strong></p>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1">
              <li><a href="/bc/">BC 专题</a> → 了解最基础的离岸公司形态（5分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/ipo/">BVI架构与境外上市</a> → 红筹架构中的BVI角色（10分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/vista/">VISTA 信托</a> → 将公司股权置入信托同时保留经营控制权（10分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/case-studies/">案例四（红筹上市）</a> → 典型架构示例（5分钟）</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="border border-border-main rounded-xl overflow-hidden group">
          <summary class="px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-bg-muted hover:bg-border-light transition-colors font-sans font-semibold text-base flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>我是律师/会计师/专业顾问</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-5 py-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
            <p><strong>你可能需要：</strong>法规索引、合规要点、争议解决参考</p>
            <p><strong>推荐阅读路径：</strong></p>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1">
              <li><a href="/economic/">经济实质法合规</a> → 完整法规解读（10分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/regulatory/">监管动态追踪</a> → 最新法规更新（5分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/calendar/">合规日历</a> → 年度节点速查（3分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/arbitration/">国际仲裁</a> + <a href="/litigation/">诉讼指南</a> → 争议解决参考（10分钟）</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="border border-border-main rounded-xl overflow-hidden group">
          <summary class="px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-bg-muted hover:bg-border-light transition-colors font-sans font-semibold text-base flex items-center justify-between">
            <span>我只是想了解一下 BVI</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-5 py-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
            <p><strong>推荐阅读路径：</strong></p>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1">
              <li><a href="/comparison/">工具对比</a> → 一张表看懂四种工具（3分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/bc/">BC 是什么</a> → 最基础的离岸公司（5分钟）</li>
              <li><a href="/about/">关于本站</a> → 网站定位和内容范围（2分钟）</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
